{"word":"Kidron","slug":"kidron","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Kidron</b> <a href=\"#/H6939\">H6939</a> <br/> Called Cedron.<br/> A valley and stream between Jerusalem and the Mount of Olives<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=37'>1Ki 2:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=2&verse=15'>Neh 2:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=31&verse=40'>Jer 31:40</a><br/> David flees from Absalom across<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=23'>2Sa 15:23</a><br/> Destruction of idols at, by Asa, Josiah, and the Levites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=13'>1Ki 15:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=6'>2Ki 23:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=12'>2Ki 23:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=29&verse=16'>2Ch 29:16</a><br/> Source of, closed by Hezekiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=32&verse=4'>2Ch 32:4</a><br/> Jesus crossed, on the night of His agony<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=1'>Joh 18:1</a>"}]}